    "This leaves little time for governance on appropriate AI usage.",
    "Meanwhile, AI text detectors like Turnitin falter against advanced language models, and students can access free AI detection tools (Williams, 2023; Tate, 2023).",
    "At this critical point, understanding which tools students use and their experiences is essential.",
    "This knowledge could assist educators in harnessing AI's potential for high-quality teaching and learning while guiding safe and effective adoptions of these technological tools.",
